name: Red fox
description:
A cute red fox made out of  silk and a synthetic copper fabric,  mounted on a black painted wood base. All details are hand embroidered with white  and black thread. A unique, one of a kind piece, ready to hang on your wall.

wood base: approx. 7 x 8" 
(the lenght of the head stoods out from the wall approx. 9")

name: Greyge deer with black antlers
description:
This pretty deer head is made out of linen, silk and velvet, mounted on a black painted wood base. All details are hand embroidered with silver and black thread. A unique, one of a kind piece, ready to hang on your wall.

wood base: approx. 7 x 8" 
Antlers : approx. 5"
(the lenght of the head stoods out from the wall approx. 9")

name: two little sheep
description:
This cute sheep is made out of linen, faux fur and vintage fabric, mounted on a round wood base. All details are hand embroidered. One of a kind piece, ready to hang on the wall.

wood base: approx. 6 x 6 "
(the head stoods from the wall approx. 10")

name: Iceberger I
description:
A little creature from the icebergs. This is a very delicate piece, made out of linen, velvet, faux fur, and  synthetic fabric, it has a silk iceberg on his tummy (different from one another), sequin  details on his shoulders and beads on his face. All details are hand embroidered. 

approx. 9 x 10 " (from ear to ear)
